snippet.title: OverTime - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
OverTime is a game about...time. You'll have to solve time puzzles and dodge the dimensional anomalies, but be fast - the clock is ticking.

You are an office worker at a company that investigates dimensional shifts. Everything goes wrong and the you have to find out what happened, fix the paradox and escape, with only the aid of a time-shifting device called the Primer Gun that allows you to go back in time and collaborate with alternate timeline versions of yourself.
